{"tid":925548,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【幾乎壞死】Botox打錯入血管 貪靚女嘴唇脹2倍差啲要切","createTime":"2018-12-02T22:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T01:39:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"df25406c7e581f473e9db2215ceaf44c81a8adae","tid":925548,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T22:01:36.000Z","msg":"英國萊斯特郡（Leicestershire）一名女子到朋友家參加「肉毒桿菌注射派對」，美容師在她上唇注射Botox時錯誤打進她的血管，令她嘴唇比正常脹大2倍，幾乎壞死。<br />\n29歲的克納皮爾（Rachael Knappier）8月尾到朋友家一同接受肉毒桿菌注射，她年輕時因撞傷面部，令嘴唇有一小腫塊。美容師就跟她說那腫塊會是她的「弱點」，令原本只打算進行前額去皺注射的克納皮爾，被說服以220鎊（約2,200港元）在嘴唇進行肉毒桿菌注射。<br />\n不過注射後數小時她的嘴唇脹大了2倍，她求醫時才發現肉毒桿菌錯誤地注射到她的動脈，令她的嘴唇腫脹，更阻擋了血液供應，幾乎令嘴唇組織死亡而要切除。3天後她接受溶解劑注射，她的嘴唇在3個月後才回復正常。<br />\n克納皮爾憶述：「當時有飲料有食物，一群女人在廚房像輸送帶般坐着等候接受注射，面上搽有麻醉藥。我當時還以為那位美容師是名護士，我沒有被問及簽署任何同意書。我應該要意識到有問題，但與朋友一起，加上派對的氣氛，令我失去警覺性。」<br />\n英國美容整形外科聯會發言人米洛瓦諾維奇（Nikki Milovanovic）警告，雖然肉毒桿菌是需要處方的藥物，但很多不擇手段的人能簡單在網上獲得肉毒桿菌。法律上，手術只能由合資格的臨床醫生注射，或在他們監督下進行。<br />\n美容安全運動發起人馬里孔達（Antonia Mariconda）敦促政府加大力度，禁止非醫護人員為他人注射肉毒桿菌。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181130/large/1543544992_6d47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181130%2Flarge%2F1543544992_6d47.jpg&h=a951e7d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"918d665f522b11e8280714bfc1aa45b240c78bb3","tid":925548,"uid":53855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T22:05:36.000Z","msg":"天地有正氣！"},{"pid":"d246a9536777f9d83817835183a4d5ce87977e6f","tid":925548,"uid":29297,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T22:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ccue.singtao.ca//Output/media/2016/10/201631018_EN_%E9%87%91%E5%89%9B_02_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fccue.singtao.ca%2F%2FOutput%2Fmedia%2F2016%2F10%2F201631018_EN_%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%2589%259B_02_0.jpg&h=939417e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a70d1e500f5a23417383bf81113982a3aa2c915","tid":925548,"uid":63909,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T22:47:29.000Z","msg":"匪話連篇<br />\n咩加大力度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb432b8ca429d5e6eb0c5f8cf9dd60186a18fd6f","tid":925548,"uid":13257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T22:52:48.000Z","msg":"為咗靚果少少，打呢d botox 已經覺得無咩為，佢仲要on9到喺一個party度打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04927a23851e152dfe8a7ebaada0c1b2ab8494d0","tid":925548,"uid":186087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T00:01:35.000Z","msg":"幾靚"},{"pid":"06dbe3942d0b4eff40975492a87b7b99fe714c53","tid":925548,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T00:40:08.000Z","msg":"Pumpkinjenn?<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NoUEQuE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNoUEQuE.png&h=05da2e08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f82e838fbae0c3217bede08520a21a83bfc8cb9","tid":925548,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T00:43:54.000Z","msg":"咁索仲整乜撚，唔撚知足，多9魚"},{"pid":"a5f8810a3a3cb400cdaee3a63d8db4cc609b51ae","tid":925548,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb432b8ca429d5e6eb0c5f8cf9dd60186a18fd6f","tid":925548,"uid":13257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T22:52:48.000Z","msg":"為咗靚果少少，打呢d botox 已經覺得無咩為，佢仲要on9到喺一個party度打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T01:39:57.000Z","msg":"理解唔到點解會係個party度打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}